Bash = Bourne again Shell
=====================

	Ø It is a default shell in most linux distributions like ubuntu and centos etc
	Ø It is a command line interpreter 
	Ø Used for :- running commands, writing shell scripts and automate any task 

Wt is a shell?
===========

	Ø Interface between user and kernel 

Ex:- bash, zsh, sh


Wt is shell script?
==============

	Ø It is a file that contains a series of commands written for the shell to execute 

